                                    <material type="stone">Sandstone</material> <note>Described as <q>pale grey, weathered deeper grey with iron staining, medium-grained sandstone...[material] of this type are exposed in the upland area adjacent to the find-site</q> (Redknap and Lewis 2007, 406).</note>
